title: Should Suns Be Worried About Pelicans?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss the Pelicans stunning win over Suns, Devin Booker’s hamstring injury, Jimmy Butler’s spicy 45-piece against the Hawks, Ja and Grizzlies even series with Timberwolves, Sixers-Raptors preview, how Kyrie should react to Boston’s crowd, the latest on Ben Simmons, plus Georgia DE Travon Walker stops by to discuss the NFL Draft and his insane combine numbers. All that and more!!!
